room_title: Escape room "Bird's Movie Zone" by Real Escape in Bakersfield
room_description: It’s 1997 and you are stuck in a video store during the Alien invasion above. Fear… Nostalgia… Strategy… Aliens…  You are the “visitors” (aka the people stuck in the store) you have 1 hour to find the store key and escape……. If only it was that simple. Can you escape in time?
